{"tid":641512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國的會爆炸】廣州17歲少女洗澡煤氣爆炸變火人 全身9成燒傷","createTime":"2018-04-25T05:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T16:18:32.000Z","uid":68902,"like":87,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2f8687b1570ec114b5165134007a3a728bee26","tid":641512,"uid":68902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:10:53.000Z","msg":"廣州一名17歲少女在家洗澡時煤氣爆炸，頓時變成「火人」，導致<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全身90%皮膚燒傷。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n就讀廣州一中高二年級的少女巫芷欣，本月19日晚在家洗澡時煤氣爆炸。廣州市民短短幾日籌集50萬元人民幣，幫助欣欣緩解了燃眉之急。廣州市紅十字會醫院昨日表示，目前巫芷欣已度過休克期，但仍未脫離危險期，預計明天開始第一次植皮手術，但小欣的治療費用仍有距離。後續修復治療預計還需2個半月，大概要7次手術，治療費用預計超過100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n廣州市紅十字會醫院燒傷整形外科副主任醫師鄧忠遠解釋，小欣屬於特重度燒傷，她被診斷為全身多處火焰燒傷90%、中度吸入性損傷、燒傷低血容量性休克和四肢燒傷焦痂肌筋膜室綜合症。<br />\n<br />\n鄧忠遠透露，她被送來時出現了氣道梗阻，有窒息風險。醫院為小欣立即做了氣管切開。為了預防骨筋膜室綜合徵，還做了上肢的切開減壓。鄧忠遠說，最難過的是感染關，並發症嚴重可能導致器官衰竭。小欣燒傷面積較大，好的皮膚不多，修復難度非常大。燒傷的很多併發症都是由創面引起的，未來計劃分步分次手術，借助生物敷料保護創面，幫助患者度過危機。<br />\n<br />\n至於為何會發生煤氣爆炸，家屬表示，家裡住宿條件較差，原本計劃近期將把煤氣罐改為管道煤氣，但沒想到突然發生了意外。小欣那天洗澡前曾表示聞到煤氣味，但大家都未料到竟然會發生爆炸。目前爆炸原因仍在調查當中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E17%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%B4%97%E6%BE%A1%E7%85%A4%E6%B0%A3%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E8%AE%8A%E7%81%AB%E4%BA%BA-%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB9%E6%88%90%E7%87%92%E5%82%B7-113700204.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25B7%259E17%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25B4%2597%25E6%25BE%25A1%25E7%2585%25A4%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2582%25B8%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%2581%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25BA%25AB9%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2587%2592%25E5%2582%25B7-113700204.html&d=i%2FJsSzWykDEOeH%2BadX%2B7WviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5839a9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E17%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%B4%97%E6%BE%A1%E7%85%A4%E6%B0%A3%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E8%AE%8A%E7%81%AB%E4%BA%BA-%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB9%E6%88%90%E7%87%92%E5%82%B7-113700204.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9成燒傷仲生存到 ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ffa0050841ca584389e5654cd0439e99b649a4","tid":641512,"uid":95397,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"真係慘過死左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6f0b5d92ab4231b97727cecf8366ceb134f378","tid":641512,"uid":99568,"like":7,"dislike":44,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e58a3663e60b3b4bf00fdaa3fa0e8c5f08a5cf","tid":641512,"uid":2455,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"醫番都晒藥費<im